(304, 1, '2018-09-05 10:12:14', '2018-09-05 10:12:14', '<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">We are a germany Based BPO looking for young, Bright and Ambitious Male/Female Customer Services Executives to join our friendly and exciting call center</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Peakstel is here to change the stereotype of call centre industry. We required candidates who put their work before anything else and want to grow and achieve something in their life. If you want to stand out of the crowd and are ready for that chance to bring about a change in your life, now is the time for you</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Peakstel is offering handsome salary packages to deserving candidates. Everyone is encouraged to apply for the job with a positive attitude to polish themselves and enable themselves to get to the top. Best environment and staff will be provided the the candidates. Our aim is to not only hire people but to make them think out of the box to get what they dreamt of.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><b>Requirements:</b></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Outbound Call Center Temp to hire position Hours: Monday - Friday, 8PM – 5AM </span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Responsibilities will include but are not limited to: </span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Providing outstanding customer service to all customers in a professional and courteous manner </span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Data and order entry </span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Handling a high volume of outbound calls </span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Reaching out to customers regarding orders, deliveries, inquires, etc. Requirements: </span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Clear and professional speaking voice/telephone manner </span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Excellent customer service skills </span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bilingual a plus </span></li><li><s