(312, 1, '2018-12-31 11:50:03', '2018-12-31 11:50:03', '<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Akara Paints Pakistan Limited, a leading paint manufacturing company is looking For “RMS Officer” in Lahore.To arrange the Short Packing Materials in advance as per requirement with the coordination, and to plan for maintaining the maximum and minimum stock level as per requirement.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Update the Bin Cards of all Raw Materials & empty gelatin capsles on daily basis and keep all records from time to time.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Major responsibilities may include.</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Responsible for timely receiving of finished goods in warehouse and total number of move orders received should be transferred with material within prescribed time after receiving.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Responsible for placement of material in shelves and accurate picking of material according to pick slips in order to reduce mismatches.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Responsible to inspect physical conditions of equipment its maintenance, repairs, or replacements.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Responsible for ensuring safety and security of material and equipment</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Skills:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Oracle ERP</span></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Candidate with at least 2 years relevant experience as Storekeeper in a in a Reputed Company. Must have experience in Mumbai Based RMC Companies. Can Join Immediately. Computer Knowledge is must. Excellent Communication & Coordination Skills.</span></p>', 'Raw Material Store Officer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'raw-material-store-officer', '', '', '2018-12-31 11:50:03', '2018-12-31 11:50:03', '', 0, 'https://demo.nokriwp.com/?post_type=job_post&amp;p=312', 0, 'job_post', '', 0),
